{"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/52786", "repository_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust", "labels_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/52786/labels{/name}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/52786/comments", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/52786/events", "html_url": "https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/52786", "id": 345320371, "node_id": "MDU6SXNzdWUzNDUzMjAzNzE=", "number": 52786, "title": "dropck unsoundness: unions are ignored", "user": {"login": "RalfJung", "id": 330628, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjMzMDYyOA==", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/330628?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/RalfJung", "html_url": "https://github.com/RalfJung", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/RalfJung/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/RalfJung/following{/other_user}", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/RalfJung/gists{/gist_id}", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/RalfJung/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/RalfJung/subscriptions", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/RalfJung/orgs", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/RalfJung/repos", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/RalfJung/events{/privacy}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/RalfJung/received_events", "type": "User", "site_admin": false}, "labels": [{"id": 171502053, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwxNzE1MDIwNTM=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/A-borrow-checker", "name": "A-borrow-checker", "color": "f7e101", "default": false, "description": "Area: The borrow checker"}, {"id": 267612997, "node_id": "MDU6TGFiZWwyNjc2MTI5OTc=", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/labels/I-unsound", "name": "I-unsound", "color": "e11d21", "default": false, "description": "Issue: A soundness hole (worst kind of bug), see: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Soundness"}], "state": "closed", "locked": false, "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "milestone": null, "comments": 4, "created_at": "2018-07-27T18:16:53Z", "updated_at": "2018-08-17T17:00:27Z", "closed_at": "2018-08-17T17:00:27Z", "author_association": "MEMBER", "active_lock_reason": null, "body": "So it turns out that [this](https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/pull/52711/files#r205711413) is a problem: The following code should be rejected by dropck, but [it compiles](https://play.rust-lang.org/?gist=c933f4631e2e46e8504b64b1d150442d&version=nightly&mode=debug&edition=2015).\r\n```rust\r\n#![feature(untagged_unions)]\r\n#![allow(unions_with_drop_fields)]\r\n\r\nuse std::cell::Cell;\r\nuse std::ops::Deref;\r\n\r\nunion Wrap<T> { x: T }\r\n\r\nimpl<T> Drop for Wrap<T>  {\r\n    fn drop(&mut self) {\r\n        unsafe { std::ptr::drop_in_place(&mut self.x as *mut _); }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nimpl<T> Wrap<T> {\r\n    fn new(x: T) -> Self {\r\n        Wrap { x }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nimpl<T> Deref for Wrap<T> {\r\n    type Target = T;\r\n    #[inline]\r\n    fn deref(&self) -> &Self::Target {\r\n        unsafe {\r\n            &self.x\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n}\r\n\r\nstruct C<'a>(Cell<Option<&'a C<'a>>>);\r\n\r\nimpl<'a> Drop for C<'a> {\r\n    fn drop(&mut self) {}\r\n}\r\n\r\nfn main() {\r\n    let v : Wrap<C> = Wrap::new(C(Cell::new(None)));\r\n    v.0.set(Some(&v));\r\n}\r\n```\r\nThis is a nightly-only (because implementing `Drop` for unions is unstable) soundness issue. I need unsafe code to exploit it, but `Wrap` above should be a perfectly safe to use type.", "closed_by": {"login": "bors", "id": 3372342, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjMzNzIzNDI=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3372342?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors", "html_url": "https://github.com/bors", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/bors/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/